title: Crime Files
subTitle: The host presents dramatised re-enactments of the country's most shocking and real-life criminal cases and their investigation.

title: Do Chutki Sindoor
subTitle: Siddhi, a dutiful girl, takes care of Maya, her sister with mental illness. However, when Maya regains her sanity, Siddhi's marriage turns troublesome.

title: Yam Kisi Se Kam Nahin
subTitle: Despite being a god, Yamraj has to constantly deal with the problems of a common man.

title: Janani
subTitle: An educated woman's career ambitions are thwarted when she's obliged to marry into a male-dominated household. However, she embarks on a mission to emancipate the women around her.

title: Agni Vayu
subTitle: Agni, a doctor, crosses paths with Vayu, an investment banker, and the two start to like each other. Together, they try to decipher the mysterious deaths of those who were close to them.

title: Dharmakshetra
subTitle: Following the Mahabharata War, the Pandavas and the Kauravas enter the court of Lord Chitragupta and answer his questions about their past actions.

title: Laal Banarasi
subTitle: Gauri, a skilled weaver and pride of the community, weaves her dreams through her art. However, a rich woman poses obstacles in her way.

title: Har Har Bhakti
subTitle: A religious leader delivers a discourse on the teachings of the holy scriptures and urges the devotees to follow the path of righteousness.

title: Paapnaashini Ganga
subTitle: Lord Brahma orders Ganga, a goddess born from the divine feet of Vishnu and sustained in Lord Shiva's locks, to bless and protect the humans on Earth.
